    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 scoping guidance. The hemolysis QoI cross-comparison demonstrates agreement within 8% against an independent high-fidelity CFD reference, which the assessment team considers functionally equivalent to experimental validation for the purposes of this COU. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all five operating points. The package is accepted for submission in support of the 510(k) hemolysis comparative analysis.",
